{"id": "1175420838800015422", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 0, "author_id": "723116696004460594", "author_name": "lunacy_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本上流程就是開超維回合後每打到剩六張就開一次詹金，像這樣的分批打", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:02:46.233000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175421087509663824", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 0, "author_id": "723116696004460594", "author_name": "lunacy_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過也是有帶歌者，配偵探裝備去一次多抽多降當作超維回合開場的小爆發", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:03:45.530000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175421168937873429", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 0, "author_id": "723116696004460594", "author_name": "lunacy_li", "author_bot": false, "content": "和用她的盾來達到必定爆擊", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:04:04.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
