{"id": "1175422978327064677", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164468851736592415", "author_name": "gaoweishengwur_01178", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過新版本更講究長遠的策略深度，打牌過程的選擇，以及更注重平衡。所以過於膨脹的機制會做調整", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:11:16.336000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175426912659718184", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 19, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "11月30日！！期待守密人加入！", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:26:54.354000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1096601777366900757"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1175407300723363950", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175426944586760342", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 19, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝幫忙解答~", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:27:01.966000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:27:07.307000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["977903961694674974"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1175415160618352700", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175427271931207731", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 19, "author_id": "1168397039999135905", "author_name": "alpha0909_", "author_bot": false, "content": "不過超維界域的特點也很明顯，基本上就是5個回合迎來一輪爆發，而其他界域，例如深海和混沌是較為平穩的傷害分佈，血肉界域是不穩定的爆發和高風險性~", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T13:28:20.011000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["723116696004460594"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1175415796659408986", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175439836430213210", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 19, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果説是我的話，會更加偏向於薩爾瓦多，因為來自血肉的神父能給人一種非常濃厚的安全感，在一測的體驗里靠著神父的盾擊流派也很輕鬆地就能拿到當時幻夢深潛的前三名，可以說無論是在強度上還是顏值上都是無可挑剔的", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T14:18:15.621000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1164468851736592415"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1175368894677000212", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1175439848673398784", "channel_id": "1131839817982947429", "type": 0, "author_id": "1170753879617572915", "author_name": "niubi.plusv587", "author_bot": false, "content": "", "timestamp": "2023-11-18T14:18:18.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
